videos.description: Cincinnati's Logan Johnson viciously throws Lawson Korita's layup off the glass, preventing an easy bucket on the fast break.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Johnson comes up with monster chasedown block

videos.description: Cincinnati's Cane Broome hits a deep two with the defense draped all over him to force overtime against Tulsa.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Broome hits clutch shot to force OT
